metadata.name: San Pedro Waves Trailer
metadata.description:
Wild Alpha, a cutting-edge music collective, has recently released a groundbreaking NFT unlike any other. This unique offering, which represents the group's inaugural release, was created by the collective's founding members.

The beats for the NFT were produced in Atlanta, GA, and the waves were captured in San Pedro, CA. Additionally, the collective incorporated AI vocal sounds that bear a striking resemblance to the artist The Weeknd, adding a fresh and exciting twist to the NFT's musical composition.

The NFT is just the first of many creative endeavors that Wild Alpha has in store for its fans. The group has been working tirelessly to create an array of innovative and boundary-pushing tracks that are sure to captivate listeners.

Join the Wild Alpha community today and stay tuned for more exciting releases from this dynamic and talented music collective.
